Notes on using URP for rendering 2d projects

It seems to be much nicer than default rendering pipeline but we can always
change between the two depending on what we need.

Resource links:
* Forum post - https://forum.unity.com/threads/2d-renderer-in-universal-render-pipeline-in-2019-3.829851/
* Samples - https://github.com/Unity-Technologies/2d-renderer-samples
